          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 8186,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "To increase the amount of time people spend on a platform, platforms detach users from reality: users lose their sense of time and are tempted to keep scrolling, watching or clicking. This approach is reminiscent of casinos, where the lack of windows and the tempting lights of slot machines keep people inside for hours, far away from the outside world. Bits of Freedom advises the European Commission to take the following measures.",
