          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 8509,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "Design elements that retain consumers’ attention should be prohibited, including a ban on the endless scroll function, and a ban on auto-playing videos, including previews;",
